item.title: Flutter Google Maps Setup
item.description: The following guide is designed to get you up and running with Google Maps in Flutter for iOS and Android, as well as device GPS tracking. Also refer to the official Flutter Google Maps Plugin setup docs as needed. Google Maps for Flutter Get your Google Maps API Key First, obtain an API key for Google Maps within the context of a Google Cloud Platform project. iOS Setup file_type_config ios/Runner/AppDelegate.m #include "AppDelegate.
